data.description: This is a beautiful 4 bed + bonus room, 2 bath 1,943sf home located in Chula Vista. Home comes with a 2 car garage and potential for RV parking on side. Kitchen recently upgraded with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. New flooring and fresh paint throughout home. Large backyard with private pool and plenty of space for gardening and family gatherings. Home centrally located to shops, restaurants, easy freeway access, and close to J street marina.
